                  <div class="section-item-title-xs-narrow text-primary">my achievements</div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-7">
                  <div class="fs18 text-grey mt5">It's always good to receive positive and constructive feedback for your work - from clients and moreover, from designers!</div>

                  <div class="mt55">
